{
  "video_id": "M0-b-z5Le10",
  "title": "How adoption worked for me | Christopher Ategeka",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 13435.0,
      "end_time": 16126.0,
      "text": "How many of you are tired"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 16674.0,
      "end_time": 21134.0,
      "text": "of seeing celebrities adopting kids from the African continent?"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 21159.0,
      "end_time": 22738.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 24342.0,
      "end_time": 26695.0,
      "text": "Well, it&#39;s not all that bad."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 28573.0,
      "end_time": 29941.0,
      "text": "I was adopted."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 31451.0,
      "end_time": 34153.0,
      "text": "I grew up in rural Uganda,"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 35495.0,
      "end_time": 38263.0,
      "text": "lost both my parents when I was very, very young."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 39978.0,
      "end_time": 41697.0,
      "text": "And when my parents passed,"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 42467.0,
      "end_time": 48608.0,
      "text": "I experienced all the negative effects of poverty,"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 49360.0,
      "end_time": 50979.0,
      "text": "from homelessness,"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 51300.0,
      "end_time": 52772.0,
      "text": "eating out of trash piles,"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 53539.0,
      "end_time": 54689.0,
      "text": "you name it."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 56603.0,
      "end_time": 58770.0,
      "text": "But my life changed"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 59380.0,
      "end_time": 62851.0,
      "text": "when I got accepted into an orphanage."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 63808.0,
      "end_time": 66155.0,
      "text": "Through one of those sponsor-an-orphan programs,"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 66924.0,
      "end_time": 70631.0,
      "text": "I was sponsored and given an opportunity to acquire an education."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 71963.0,
      "end_time": 74730.0,
      "text": "I started off in Uganda."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 74970.0,
      "end_time": 77851.0,
      "text": "I went through school, and the way this particular program worked,"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 77875.0,
      "end_time": 80830.0,
      "text": "you finished high school and after high school,"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 80107.0,
      "end_time": 83767.0,
      "text": "you go learn a trade -- to become a carpenter, a mechanic"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 83791.0,
      "end_time": 85591.0,
      "text": "or something along those lines."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 86559.0,
      "end_time": 89426.0,
      "text": "My case was a little different."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 90308.0,
      "end_time": 94401.0,
      "text": "The sponsor family that was sending these 25 dollars a month"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 94425.0,
      "end_time": 96837.0,
      "text": "to this orphanage to sponsor me,"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 96861.0,
      "end_time": 98713.0,
      "text": "which -- I had never met them --"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 99702.0,
      "end_time": 101536.0,
      "text": "said, \"Well ..."
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 102813.0,
      "end_time": 105419.0,
      "text": "we would like to send you to college instead.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 106538.0,
      "end_time": 107765.0,
      "text": "Oh -- it gets better."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 107790.0,
      "end_time": 108833.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 108857.0,
      "end_time": 111693.0,
      "text": "And they said, \"If you get the paperwork,"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 111717.0,
      "end_time": 114620.0,
      "text": "we&#39;ll send you to school in America instead.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 116856.0,
      "end_time": 118443.0,
      "text": "So with their help,"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 119287.0,
      "end_time": 122583.0,
      "text": "I went to the embassy and applied for the visa."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 123216.0,
      "end_time": 124604.0,
      "text": "I got the visa."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 124629.0,
      "end_time": 128660.0,
      "text": "I remember this day like it was yesterday."
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 129539.99999999999,
      "end_time": 132418.0,
      "text": "I walked out of the embassy with this piece of paper in my hand,"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 132442.0,
      "end_time": 134157.0,
      "text": "a hop in my step,"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 134181.0,
      "end_time": 135882.0,
      "text": "smile on my face,"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 135906.0,
      "end_time": 139293.0,
      "text": "knowing that my life is about to change."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 140875.0,
      "end_time": 142465.0,
      "text": "I went home that night,"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 143168.0,
      "end_time": 144982.0,
      "text": "and I slept with my passport,"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 145600.0,
      "end_time": 147313.0,
      "text": "because I was afraid that someone might steal it."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 147337.0,
      "end_time": 149191.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 149216.0,
      "end_time": 150636.0,
      "text": "I couldn&#39;t fall asleep."
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 151446.0,
      "end_time": 152764.0,
      "text": "I kept feeling it."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 153896.0,
      "end_time": 155725.0,
      "text": "I had a good idea for security."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 156324.0,
      "end_time": 158893.0,
      "text": "I was like, \"OK, I&#39;m going to put it in a plastic bag,"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 158917.0,
      "end_time": 162424.0,
      "text": "and take it outside and dig a hole, and put it in there.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 163706.0,
      "end_time": 165650.0,
      "text": "I did that, went back in the house."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 165675.0,
      "end_time": 168628.0,
      "text": "I could not fall asleep. I was like, \"Maybe someone saw me.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 168652.0,
      "end_time": 169803.0,
      "text": "I went back --"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 169827.0,
      "end_time": 170837.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 170861.0,
      "end_time": 173635.0,
      "text": "I pulled it out, and I put it with me the entire night --"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 173659.0,
      "end_time": 176617.0,
      "text": "all to say that it was an anxiety-filled night."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 176641.0,
      "end_time": 177791.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 178203.0,
      "end_time": 182254.0,
      "text": "Going to the US was, just like another speaker said,"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 182278.0,
      "end_time": 184632.0,
      "text": "was my first time to see a plane,"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 184656.0,
      "end_time": 188170.0,
      "text": "be on one, let alone sit on it to fly to another country."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 189172.0,
      "end_time": 191680.0,
      "text": "December 15, 2006."
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 192610.0,
      "end_time": 193951.0,
      "text": "7:08pm."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 194580.0,
      "end_time": 197549.0,
      "text": "I sat in seat 7A."
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 198900.0,
      "end_time": 199351.0,
      "text": "Fly Emirates."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 201427.0,
      "end_time": 205105.0,
      "text": "One of the most gorgeous, beautiful women I&#39;ve ever seen walked up,"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 206246.0,
      "end_time": 209520.0,
      "text": "red little hat with a white veil."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 209792.0,
      "end_time": 212725.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m looking terrified, I have no idea what I&#39;m doing."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 213391.0,
      "end_time": 215617.0,
      "text": "She hands me this warm towel --"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 215641.0,
      "end_time": 217721.0,
      "text": "warm, steamy, snow white."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 219686.0,
      "end_time": 222000.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m looking at this warm towel;"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 222240.0,
      "end_time": 225418.0,
      "text": "I don&#39;t know what to do with my life, let alone with this damn towel --"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 225442.0,
      "end_time": 227319.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 227343.0,
      "end_time": 230161.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 231712.0,
      "end_time": 233510.0,
      "text": "I did one of the --"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 233750.0,
      "end_time": 235565.0,
      "text": "you know, anything anyone could do in that situation:"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 236430.0,
      "end_time": 238740.0,
      "text": "look around, see what everyone else is doing."
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 238764.0,
      "end_time": 239948.0,
      "text": "I did the same."
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 240549.0,
      "end_time": 245586.0,
      "text": "Mind you, I drove about seven hours from my village to the airport that day."
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 246524.0,
      "end_time": 248574.0,
      "text": "So I grab this warm towel,"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 248598.0,
      "end_time": 251743.0,
      "text": "wipe my face just like everyone else is doing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 251767.0,
      "end_time": 253213.0,
      "text": "I look at it --"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 253237.0,
      "end_time": 254402.0,
      "text": "damn."
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 254426.0,
      "end_time": 255917.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 256983.0,
      "end_time": 258821.0,
      "text": "It was all dirt brown."
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 258845.00000000003,
      "end_time": 259995.00000000003,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 260940.0,
      "end_time": 266195.0,
      "text": "I remember being so embarrassed that when she came by to pick it up,"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 266219.0,
      "end_time": 267445.0,
      "text": "I didn&#39;t give mine."
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 267470.0,
      "end_time": 268587.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 268611.0,
      "end_time": 269779.0,
      "text": "I still have it."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 269803.0,
      "end_time": 271474.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 271498.0,
      "end_time": 273468.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 274950.0,
      "end_time": 277888.0,
      "text": "Going to America opened doors for me"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 277912.0,
      "end_time": 280801.0,
      "text": "to live up to my full God-given potential."
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 281862.0,
      "end_time": 283391.0,
      "text": "I remember when I arrived,"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 283415.0,
      "end_time": 285380.0,
      "text": "the sponsor family embraced me,"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 285404.0,
      "end_time": 288733.0,
      "text": "and they literally had to teach me everything from scratch:"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 288757.0,
      "end_time": 291505.0,
      "text": "this is a microwave, that&#39;s a refrigerator --"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 291529.0,
      "end_time": 294238.0,
      "text": "things I&#39;d never seen before."
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 294262.0,
      "end_time": 296110.0,
      "text": "And it was also the first time"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 296350.0,
      "end_time": 299397.0,
      "text": "I got immersed into a new and different culture."
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 300159.0,
      "end_time": 303498.0,
      "text": "These strangers showed me"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 304381.0,
      "end_time": 305895.0,
      "text": "true love."
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 307800.0,
      "end_time": 310782.0,
      "text": "These strangers showed me that I mattered,"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 312380.0,
      "end_time": 314425.0,
      "text": "that my dreams mattered."
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 322165.0,
      "end_time": 326444.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 328841.0,
      "end_time": 329991.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 332708.0,
      "end_time": 335955.0,
      "text": "These individuals had two of their own biological children."
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 336479.0,
      "end_time": 339246.0,
      "text": "And when I came in, I had needs."
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 339691.0,
      "end_time": 341763.0,
      "text": "They had to teach me English,"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 341788.0,
      "end_time": 344572.0,
      "text": "teach me literally everything,"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 344596.0,
      "end_time": 347323.0,
      "text": "which resulted in them spending a lot of time with me."
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 347726.0,
      "end_time": 353160.0,
      "text": "And that created a little bit of jealousy with their children."
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 355155.0,
      "end_time": 359664.0,
      "text": "So, if you&#39;re a parent in this room,"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 359688.0,
      "end_time": 362697.0,
      "text": "and you have those teenager children"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 362721.0,
      "end_time": 367750.0,
      "text": "who don&#39;t want anything to do with your love and affection --"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 367990.0,
      "end_time": 368926.0,
      "text": "in fact, they find it repulsive --"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 369701.0,
      "end_time": 371254.0,
      "text": "I got a solution:"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 371278.0,
      "end_time": 372650.0,
      "text": "adopt a child."
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 372674.0,
      "end_time": 373686.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 373710.0,
      "end_time": 374950.0,
      "text": "It will solve the problem."
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 374974.0,
      "end_time": 377104.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 379274.0,
      "end_time": 381904.0,
      "text": "I went on to acquire two engineering degrees"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 381928.0,
      "end_time": 384398.0,
      "text": "from one of the best institutions in the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 385173.0,
      "end_time": 386438.0,
      "text": "I&#39;ve got to tell you:"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 386462.0,
      "end_time": 388279.0,
      "text": "talent is universal,"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 388303.0,
      "end_time": 390465.0,
      "text": "but opportunities are not."
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 391738.0,
      "end_time": 393159.0,
      "text": "And I credit this"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 394296.0,
      "end_time": 397844.0,
      "text": "to the individuals who embrace multiculturalism,"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 398747.0,
      "end_time": 400556.0,
      "text": "love, empathy"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 400580.0,
      "end_time": 402534.0,
      "text": "and compassion for others."
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 404572.0,
      "end_time": 407574.0,
      "text": "We live in a world filled with hate:"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 407598.0,
      "end_time": 409196.0,
      "text": "building walls,"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 409220.0,
      "end_time": 410514.0,
      "text": "Brexit,"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 410538.0,
      "end_time": 414170.0,
      "text": "xenophobia here on the African continent."
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 415326.0,
      "end_time": 417726.0,
      "text": "Multiculturalism can be an answer"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 417750.0,
      "end_time": 421376.0,
      "text": "to many of these worst human qualities."
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 423308.0,
      "end_time": 426960.0,
      "text": "Today, I challenge you"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 426120.0,
      "end_time": 430340.0,
      "text": "to help a young child experience multiculturalism."
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 431165.0,
      "end_time": 435248.0,
      "text": "I guarantee you that will enrich their life,"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 435272.0,
      "end_time": 436914.0,
      "text": "and in turn,"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 436939.0,
      "end_time": 438317.0,
      "text": "it will enrich yours."
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 439519.0,
      "end_time": 441183.0,
      "text": "And as a bonus,"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 441207.0,
      "end_time": 443219.0,
      "text": "one of them may even give a TED Talk."
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 443244.0,
      "end_time": 444727.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 445269.0,
      "end_time": 447634.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 450218.0,
      "end_time": 455140.0,
      "text": "We may not be able to solve the bigotry and the racism of this world today,"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 455164.0,
      "end_time": 458868.0,
      "text": "but certainly we can raise children"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 459772.0,
      "end_time": 463270.0,
      "text": "to create a positive, inclusive, connected world"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 463810.0,
      "end_time": 465387.0,
      "text": "full of empathy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 466290.0,
      "end_time": 467568.0,
      "text": "love"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 467592.0,
      "end_time": 468882.0,
      "text": "and compassion."
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 469361.0,
      "end_time": 470533.0,
      "text": "Love wins."
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 470557.0,
      "end_time": 471707.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 471731.0,
      "end_time": 474770.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}